org.qbroker.monitor

Class DummyAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.qbroker.monitor.DummyAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MonitorAction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ShortJob

    public class DummyAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements MonitorAction
    DummyAction is a dummy action only. The actions will be invoked on the event only if the status is OCCURRED. However, the event will be sent out up to tolerance times with QuietPeriod support.
    Author:
    yannanlu@yahoo.com
